47
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:22,000
the most popular of these was Penny Arcade,

48
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:24,000
a comic still going to this day,

49
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:27,000
rife with hilarious and well-thought-out humor.

50
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:29,000
Don't state me, bro! Ha ha ha!

