73
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:22,000
by reusing the same tropes.

74
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:25,000
An explosion in the gaming webcomic had begun,

75
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:27,000
and it would continue for over a decade.

76
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:30,000
